{"tid":648350,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"GPU保養問題","createTime":"2018-04-30T15:12:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-30T03:03:32.000Z","uid":180905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"af59d4e95b2e2536b5114ae22aef0ae2e332bdd9","tid":648350,"uid":180905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T15:12:06.000Z","msg":"想問下，除佐張卡燒佐開唔到機之外<br />\n其實仲有咩原因可以走去保養整張卡架呢？<br />\n<br />\n我頭先做下research見到有人話<br />\n新機得10幾20FPS, 發現係GPU VRAM頻率奇低，出佐問題<br />\n咁就拎佐去原廠搞<br />\n<br />\n咁除佐新卡有問顯<br />\n用到燒佐出問題之外仲有冇其他原因會拎番廠整？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我咁問係因為我張960好似有老化既現象<br />\n<br />\n係冇搞過d乜既情況下，平時玩PUBG有7-80FPS<br />\n但近呢2星期得番4-50FPS, 都跌得幾多所以想問下會唔會可以check到d咩問題做到保養維修下佢？<br />\n<br />\n我當時一次過砌佐3部一樣既機<br />\n佢地都keep到6-70FPS<br />\n我部機就得番4-50<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSpec:<br />\nI7 8700<br />\nZ370<br />\n8GB DDR4 3000MHz x2<br />\nIntel 760p 256GB M.2<br />\nWD 1TB<br />\nAntec NX550"},{"pid":"a54455c2ea77c8abe605a1af97ca6f22ccc08130","tid":648350,"uid":87428,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T15:12:51.000Z","msg":"買個張啦"},{"pid":"bed2b752b3af5298af04340681c2a838fed64704","tid":648350,"uid":180905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a54455c2ea77c8abe605a1af97ca6f22ccc08130","tid":648350,"uid":87428,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T15:12:51.000Z","msg":"買個張啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T15:17:22.000Z","msg":"我想佢捱到20系出再換2060/2070<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw, 補充番，張卡用佐2年，以前玩過witcher3, L4D2, overwatch, R6等等，冇乜比我大chur過，當然都冇掘過礦<br />\n<br />\n近排就玩佐大半年PUBG<br />\n呢2個月有OC過<br />\n本身係4GB GAMING OC版<br />\n有用kombuster試佢水位先OC，clock +120, memory +300<br />\n應該係安全OC"},{"pid":"ad1182edfda54f10ba48c177d9ac506e36981593","tid":648350,"uid":4754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T15:43:30.000Z","msg":"過熱？"},{"pid":"e5544b0bca7687746428885f267